data.description: ** PRICE IMPROVEMENT **. Welcome to 208 South Mont Valla Avenue! Discover the perfect blend of comfort and convenience in this spacious 4-bedroom, 2.5-bathroom residence on a 0.14-acre lot, ideally situated in Hagerstown, MD.  Located within a five-minute drive of major commuter routes and the vibrant heart of downtown Hagerstown. This stunning home boasts a main-level primary bedroom, while two additional bedrooms are located upstairs, and a bonus fourth bedroom awaits you in the basement! Upon entering the home, you'll find the living room to your left, an inviting space with a timeless appeal. Continuing through the home, to the right of the living room, you'll find a well-designed and functional kitchen. In addition to the kitchen, the main level also features a convenient half bath, making it perfect for everyday living and entertaining guests. The rich hardwood flooring on the main and upstairs levels not only adds warmth but also provides a seamless and enduring backdrop for your personal style. Upstairs, you'll find two inviting bedrooms, offering comfortable and private spaces for family members or guests. The full bath on this level is beautifully designed with modern fixtures and style, catering to the needs of the upper level of the house. But that's not all; this home also boasts a partially finished basement that adds to its appeal. The finished area is carpeted, creating a versatile space for a variety of uses.  One of the notable features of the basement is its easy access to the backyard, which adds to the convenience of outdoor living and makes it a perfect spot for barbecues and outdoor gatherings. Downstairs, you'll also have access to the utility area, where the washer and dryer are located, providing the utmost convenience for your laundry needs. This downstairs space not only adds practicality to your daily life but also enhances the overall functionality of the home. This property is a must-see, combining modern comforts with a prime location in Hagerstown, MD. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house your new home sweet home! Schedule a showing today and experience the charm and comfort this home has to offer!!
